title: MobileDevHacker:  Past Trends and Future Bets
desc: Making Apps is hard! Gather with MobileDevHacker's all star lineup to hear, mingle, and discuss topics that drive serious growth. This is a no joke collection of topics that confront app executives and developers alike. See how the industry attacks some of the toughest challenges of the past, and the future bets they'll be making.
